{"tid":851113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"菲律賓總統杜特爾特訪港 早上酒店戒備森嚴","createTime":"2018-10-07T01:49:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T03:24:57.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ef6fd5704c34ad9744a4037a966d470ac052c818","tid":851113,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T01:49:25.000Z","msg":"菲律賓總統杜特爾特（Rodrigo Duterte）早前表示可能罹患癌症，但未知目前的健康狀況，正等候檢查結果。據悉，杜特爾特近日低調到訪香港，有傳他來港目的與其健康狀況有關。<br />\n據外電報道，杜特爾特昨日由數名保鑣陪同在銅鑼灣Uniqlo出現，當時他戴上黑色口罩及鴨舌帽，與太太及女兒一同購物。其後杜特爾特的特別助理Bong Go於周六晚上10時上載數張相片到facebook，清楚見到杜特爾特在保鑣的陪同下於銅鑼灣逛街，其中更有杜特爾特與太太、女兒及特別助理的自拍照。<br />\n據悉，杜特爾特下榻灣仔君悅酒店，香港警方派出大批警員在港灣道一帶駐守及巡邏。<br />\n菲律賓文官長Salvador Medialdea確定菲律賓總統杜特爾與太太Honeylet Avance&ntilde;as、女兒Kitty及特別助理Bong Go在周五晚上由菲律賓來港作一短暫休息(weekend break)，大約逗留3日，預計周日返回菲律賓。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181006/58765474\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181006%2F58765474&d=VXAYx0S8Fq2ve3j0i6Iwn54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=e7defd5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181006%2F58765474&h=b50ea0ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181006/58765474</a>"},{"pid":"72a551acfb4116e54870f60e53582f3becc56bc5","tid":851113,"uid":142888,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T01:58:24.000Z","msg":"去日本好過啦，香港冇嘢行又迫"},{"pid":"983599ddeb252724be713f47d50d2a38bf093739","tid":851113,"uid":132587,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T02:00:35.000Z","msg":"班垃圾仲敢黎香港 <br />\n菲律賓無一個係無辜 唔好以為無人記得你地點wfc當年人質單野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"047467fc505bb6ca267d268a63debcc508ad05ea","tid":851113,"uid":209487,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T02:00:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d